children.name: Effects
children.text:
You can activate this rune after making a successful melee or ranged weapon attack to add 2d6 thunder damage to the attack's normal damage.
- This rune can be activated once and then vanishes.
- When this rune is activated, you gain 
5 temp HP
- While carrying one or more runes you gain +1 AC
- You can carry a number of runes equal to your Proficiency Bonus
